  "helpFaq1Q": "How do I cancel a field booking and get a refund?",
  "helpFaq1A": "You can cancel and receive a full refund to your wallet if you cancel at least 24 hours before the booking time. Go to \"My Tickets\" > \"Details\" > \"Cancel Booking\".",
  "helpFaq2Q": "How does the match fee (Qatta) system work?",
  "helpFaq2A": "The Qatta system lets you split the field cost among all players joining the match. Each player's share is deducted from their wallet once they confirm joining — no need to pay the full amount upfront.",
  "helpFaq3Q": "Can I add players from outside the app to a tournament?",
  "helpFaq3A": "To ensure tournament quality and integrity, all participating players must be registered in the app and officially added to your team roster to be approved by the tournament organizer.",
  "helpFaq4Q": "How do I withdraw my wallet balance?",
  "helpFaq4A": "You can withdraw your balance to your registered bank account, provided the withdrawable balance exceeds 100 SAR. The transfer takes 2 to 3 business days.",
